window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>A two-time winner of the Coretta Scott King Award, Sharon Draper has penned numerous modern classics of youth literature. The third installment of her acclaimed Jericho trilogy, <i>Just Another Hero</i> returns to familiar territory for a new spin on her indelible characters.</p><p>Arielle Gresham is faced with numerous problems at home, and a rash of petty crimes has beset her school. After alienating just about everyone who could help her, Arielle makes a fateful decision to help solve these crimes.</p>"; 
